A new species of Megischus Brullé (Hymenoptera, Stephanidae) from China, with a key to the Chinese speciesAbstract A new species of Megischus Brullé from China, Megischus aplicatus sp. n.,is described and illustrated. A key to the Chinese species of Megischus is added. The holotype is deposited in the Parasitic Hymenoptera Collection of Zhejiang University, Hangzhou.